---
source: crates/splitter-cli/tests/help_snapshots.rs
expression: output
---
Enumerate all audio input and output devices available on the host
and print them to stdout with their index and display name.

Use the reported indices or names as arguments to --input / --output / --from / --to
in other subcommands.

Example:
splitter-cli devices

Usage: splitter-cli devices

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
